{"atom_id":"md_dmRS_ex_a033","file":"knowledge_base/domains/RS/examples.md","line_start":50,"line_end":50,"parent_section":"§RS.1.3 [Example 3]","atom_type":"SENTENCE","verbatim":"**Row 1:** Shows disease progression on or after a prior chemotherapy regimen. The date of progression is represented in RSDTC. RSENTPT and RSENRTPT represent that the disease progression was prior to screening. RSCAT = \"UNSPECIFIED\" indicates that the criteria used to determine the disease progression was unknown or not collected. RSPLNKGRP = \"CM1\" is used to link this record in RS to the prior chemotherapy in CM where the CMLNKGRP = \"CM1\".","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt_version":"P0_writer_md_v1.9.2","ts":"2026-05-07T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"md_dmRS_ex_a034","file":"knowledge_base/domains/RS/examples.md","line_start":51,"line_end":51,"parent_section":"§RS.1.3 [Example 3]","atom_type":"SENTENCE","verbatim":"**Row 2:** Shows best response to prior chemotherapy regimen. The date of best response is represented in RSDTC. RSENTPT and RSENRTPT represent that the best response was prior to screening. RSCAT = \"UNSPECIFIED\" indicates that the criteria used to determine the best response was unknown or not collected. RSPLNKGRP = \"CM2\" is used to link this record in RS to the prior chemotherapy in CM where the CMLNKGRP = \"CM2\".","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt_version":"P0_writer_md_v1.9.2","ts":"2026-05-07T00:00:00Z"}}
